---------------
Release 1.2.0.9
---------------

This is a maintenance release for VIVIPOS Application (VIVIECR) 1.2.0.x

Previous 1.2.0.x releases may be upgraded to this release by installing the release XPI through the Add-on Manager.


------------
Dependencies
------------

This release requires VIVIPOS WebApp and WebServices Release 1.2.0.5 or above. You should also install Release 1.2.0.8 of the appropriate language pack to resolve translation-related bugs.


----------
Known bugs
----------

Bug #159:
    Application may wait indefinitely if connection to printer is lost while printing


----------
Bugs fixed
----------

Bug #353:
    Path used in restoring from remote media is incorrect

Bug #390:
    Shift Change fails after confirming to proceed

Bug #391:
    VFD display is incorrect for pushing and pulling orders to and from the queue

Bug #393:
    When multiple encodings are in use in device configuration, the first encountered encoding is always used to determine the printed length of the template.

